original_title: TNA One Night Only: World Cup of Wrestling 2013
overview: Teams of wrestlers from around the World compete in Heavyweight, X Division, Tag Team and Knockouts Division matches to crown the TNA World Cup of Wrestling Champions. It took place on March 18, 2013, from the Impact Wrestling Zone in Orlando, Florida and Aired on PPV on December 6, 2013.
title: TNA One Night Only: World Cup of Wrestling 2013
